			<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/artificial-intelligence-system-learns-the-fundamental-laws-of-quantum-mechanics/" class="image-link media-ratio ratio-16-9" title="Artificial Intelligence System Learns the Fundamental Laws of Quantum Mechanics"><span data-bgsrc="https://scitechdaily.com/images/Artificial-Intelligence-Quantum-Mechanics-777x518.jpg" class="img bg-cover wp-post-image attachment-large size-large lazyload" data-bgset="https://scitechdaily.com/images/Artificial-Intelligence-Quantum-Mechanics-777x518.jpg 777w, https://scitechdaily.com/images/Artificial-Intelligence-Quantum-Mechanics-400x267.jpg 400w, https://scitechdaily.com/images/Artificial-Intelligence-Quantum-Mechanics-768x512.jpg 768w, https://scitechdaily.com/images/Artificial-Intelligence-Quantum-Mechanics-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://scitechdaily.com/images/Artificial-Intelligence-Quantum-Mechanics.jpg 2000w" data-sizes="(max-width: 377px) 100vw, 377px" role="img" aria-label="Artificial Intelligence Quantum Mechanics"></span></a>			
			
			
			
		
